    <note>Guo(1) Liangchen [17987] He held an official title. He was a good friend of Lv Zuqian [7055] and together they built the Xiyuan shuyuan. A person with a mingzi that was the same as his zi (Delin) was Jinghu Nan tiju in ca. 1193, but I am assuming that they were different people since there is also an edict of appointment for a Delin in CBD, 3, 2150 [this person not entered into the dataset]. Ye Shi, WJ, 13.245-6. CBD, 3, 2136.</note>
